  "title": "Operation Director (Food Industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 6 days working day</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage and oversee the operations of units achieving financial goals</li>\n  <li>Ability to development long and short term plan</li>\n  <li>Manage, build and maintain cordial relationship</li>\n  <li>Conduct Monthly Business Review and Quarterly Business Review </li>\n  <li>Lead and achieve customer’s satisfactory survey</li>\n  <li>Achieve KPI </li>\n  <li>Lead &amp; supervise a team of staff to achieve goals</li>\n  <li>Instill training and building people capability</li>\n  <li>Responsible for the respective sector financial performance</li>\n  <li>Uphold the Group’s Health, Safety &amp; Environment (HSE) standards</li>\n  <li>Ensure high level of food quality is served at the units</li>\n  <li>Responsible for the scheduling and deployment of manpower to ensure smooth operations</li>\n  <li>Requires travelling to multiples units</li>\n  <li>Perform administrative duties</li>\n  <li>Ability to execute  Business Continuity</li>\n  <li><u><strong>Health and Safety Responsibilities:</strong></u></li>\n  <li>Follow health, safety and security procedures</li>\n  <li>Maintain safe personal presentation standards</li>\n  <li>Consult on health and safety matters</li>\n  <li>Report all incidents and hazards immediately</li>\n  <li>Complete all required HSE training</li>\n  <li>Adhere to the site food safety plan, hygiene procedures and standards</li>\n  <li><u><strong>HSE Policy / Procedure Documents:</strong></u></li>\n  <li>Health, Safety and Environment Policy</li>\n  <li>Employee Health, Safety and Environment Handbook</li>\n  <li>Relevant Inspection Forms / SOPs / PWI</li>\n  <li>Material Safety Data Sheet (MSDS)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
